      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);line-height:1.7;max-width:600px;">TopCasinoScout is fully independent. We're funded by affiliate commissions but operators cannot buy favourable reviews, higher rankings, or a better verdict. Our editorial team uses a strict scoring methodology — every casino earns its place.</p>
